name: Super pets Super spa
description:
Game made for the GDevelop Game Jam #2.

You're an employee of Super pets Super spa, every time a customer arrives take his order and follow it to make the best score. You have 5 minutes to get the highest score!

Sadly, the game has more than 1,000 elements so you will have to play them from Liluo here: https://liluo.io/luisalfredo92/super-pets-super-spa
